{"article_id":"hkXrZeOCFWTE2LXj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump crushed his opponents Tuesday night en route to a major victory in New York ' s Republican presidential primary ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"scoring a needed boost after a string of setbacks","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and putting himself back in the driver ' s seat","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"as the campaign nears the final stretch .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Networks called the race","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"seconds after polls closed at 9 p.m. ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"based on exit polling","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that showed the billionaire businessman","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"winning a majority of the vote in a state for the first time this year .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Ohio Gov . John Kasich was second ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"with Sen. Ted Cruz of Texas","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"- Mr. Trump ' s closest rival in the hunt for delegates -","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"a disappointing third .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Cruz ' s poor showing also ensures","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"he won ' t be able to win enough pledged delegates","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to guarantee victory on the first ballot at the Republican National Convention in Cleveland in July .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s big victory puts him tantalizingly close to the pathway","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that would give him the needed 1,237 delegates","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"needed","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to clinch a win on the first round .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Both parties ' races will stay in the Northeast , with a slate of five contests next week in Connecticut , Delaware , Pennsylvania , Rhode Island and Maryland - territory","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that should be friendly to Mr. Trump .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"\" We don ' t have much of a race anymore","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"based on what I ' m seeing on television , \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"an ebullient Mr. Trump said at his victory party at his Trump Tower building in Manhattan .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"\" We are really , really rocking . \"","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"With just under 60 percent of the vote counted ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Mr. Trump received 60.3 percent of the vote to 24.9 percent for Mr. Kasich and 14.9 percent for Mr. Cruz .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Mr. Trump automatically claimed 14 of the state ' s 95 delegates up for grabs","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"by winning a clear majority statewide","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and was likely to win a huge majority of the remaining delegates","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that are apportioned","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"according to results in the state ' s 27 congressional districts .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":3},{"id":34,"text":"Hillary Clinton , Bernie Sanders locked in tight race in New York primary","depth":3},{"id":35,"text":"New York is home territory for Mr. Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"who was born in Queens ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"grew up in the city","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"and has based his massive business empire there .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"During the two-week campaign","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"leading up to the vote ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"he defended \" New York values , \"","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"complained about ill treatment at the hands of the Republican Party ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"questioned Mr. Kasich ' s continued candidacy","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"and mocked Mr. Cruz .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"As results rolled in ,","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"Mr. Trump was able to claim bragging rights","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"by running up a bigger percentage of the vote in his home state","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"than did either Mr. Cruz ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"who took 44 percent in Texas ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and Mr. Kasich ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"who won 47 percent of Ohio .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The winner tried to hammer home a message","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that his momentum was unstoppable .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" We don ' t have much of a race anymore , \"","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Trump said in surprisingly brief remarks .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"He shied away from the brash talk","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that has characterized his campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"instead reprising his criticism of Republicans ' nomination process","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and predicting smooth sailing ahead in the upcoming primaries .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Campaigning in Pennsylvania ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Cruz projected confidence in his campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"insisting","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"he is the true \" outsider \" candidates","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"restive Republican voters are looking for this year .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"He also tried to tie himself to Mr. Sanders , the self-professed Democratic socialist","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"who has shaken up the Democratic race ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"they both share an anti-establishment approach to campaigning","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that eschews special interests .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Cruz also embraced President Obama ' s 2008 campaign slogan , \" Yes we can , \"","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"it ' s time","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to turn that hope into \" another giant leap for mankind . \"","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"\" Join me on this journey of less talk and more action , \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the senator said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"With 1,237 the target number , Mr. Trump entered the evening with 756 convention delegates ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Mr. Cruz had 559","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"and Mr. Kasich trailed far behind at 144 .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"There were 95 delegates at stake in New York ,","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"while Mr. Trump was poised to win the vast majority ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"it was too early to calculate his exact total ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"which depends on a complex formula","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"based on results in each of the state ' s congressional districts .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Mr. Kasich has long been mathematically eliminated from winning the nomination on the first ballot at the national convention ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"and analysts said","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Mr. Cruz is nearing that point .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Indeed , it ' s now impossible for him to win enough pledged delegates","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"- meaning those","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"required by party rules","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"to support him -","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"ahead of the convention .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"That means he and Mr. Kasich are now both forced to pursue victory","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"by trying to sway \" unbound \" delegates and those","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"already committed to someone else","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"while trying to deny Mr. Trump a first-round win .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Tuesday ' s results also dented the momentum","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"Mr. Cruz had built in recent weeks .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"He scored an easy win this month in Wisconsin ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"and his formidable campaign organization helped him win delegates at Colorado ' s district conventions and Wyoming ' s county conventions .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Stung by those results","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Mr. Trump shook up his campaign in recent weeks ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"adding longtime Republican Party operatives to his staff .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"That did not sit well with some of his longtime staffers ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"including Stuart Jolly , his national field director ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"who resigned amid the shuffle .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"\" It ' s actually a team of unity ;","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"it ' s evolving , \"","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Mr. Trump said Tuesday night ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"accusing the press of misrepresenting what he is doing .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Despite his success on the campaign trail ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Republican Party leaders remain spooked by the prospect of Mr. Trump as their nominee .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"Indeed , Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , Kentucky Republican , seemed this week to be praying for an extended convention","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"that could deny Mr. Trump the nod ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"he wanted to see a second or third ballot .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"On Tuesday , he said","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"he had \" inartfully \" expressed himself","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"but didn ' t deny","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"that he was trying to derail the New Yorker ' s outsider bid .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"\" We ' ll have a nominee","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"once we get to 1,237 votes .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"if that does not happen on the first ballot ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"there will be another ballot .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"And I hope","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"that out of this process ,","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"no matter when it ends","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"- first , second , third or additional ballots -","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"we ' ll have a nominee","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"who will be appealing to the American people","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and can actually win the election , \"","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Mr. McConnell said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":267,"left":168,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":166,"right":167,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":166,"left":153,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":137,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":0,"right":136,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":1,"right":135,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":148,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":141,"right":147,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":138,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":6,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":144,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":143,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":142,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":13,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":16,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":17,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":158,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left"